---
title: Caribbean Style BBQ Pork Loaded Wedges with Pepper, Onion and Cheese
description: This Caribbean Style BBQ Pork Loaded Wedges is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
